    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一、填空题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            57,
            132,
            148,
            147
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 $\\frac{\\mathrm{e}^{x + y} - y\\sin(xy)}{x\\sin(xy) - \\mathrm{e}^{x + y}}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            154,
            316,
            186
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\mathrm{e}^{x + y} + \\cos (xy) = 0$ 两边对 $x$ 求导得",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            193,
            452,
            207
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\mathrm{e}^{x + y}\\cdot \\left(1 + \\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}}\\right) - \\sin (xy)\\cdot \\left(y + x\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}}\\right) = 0$ ，解得 $\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} = \\frac{\\mathrm{e}^{x + y} - y\\sin(xy)}{x\\sin(xy) - \\mathrm{e}^{x + y}}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            217,
            708,
            247
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 $\\left\\{\\frac{2}{9}, \\frac{4}{9}, -\\frac{4}{9}\\right\\}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            255,
            309,
            284
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial x} = \\frac{2x}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}, \\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial y} = \\frac{2y}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}, \\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial z} = \\frac{2z}{x^2 + y^2 + z^2},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            294,
            704,
            323
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\left.\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial x}\\right|_{M} = \\frac{2}{9},\\quad \\left.\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial y}\\right|_{M} = \\frac{4}{9},\\quad \\left.\\frac{\\partial u}{\\partial z}\\right|_{M} = -\\frac{4}{9}$ 则 $\\mathbf{grad}u\\Big|_M = \\left\\{\\frac{2}{9},\\frac{4}{9}, - \\frac{4}{9}\\right\\} .$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            333,
            750,
            362
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【答案】 $\\frac{\\pi^2}{2}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            372,
            202,
            399
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $f(x)$ 的傅里叶级数在 $x = \\pi$ 处收敛于",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            409,
            469,
            423
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {f (\\pi - 0) + f (\\pi + 0)}{2} = \\frac {f (\\pi - 0) + f (- \\pi + 0)}{2} = \\frac {\\pi^ {2}}{2}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            283,
            431,
            739,
            461
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4)【答案】 $y = (x + C)\\cos x$ （ $C$ 为任意常数）.",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            468,
            460,
            484
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 微分方程 $y' + y \\tan x = \\cos x$ 的通解为",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            489,
            485,
            503
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$y = \\left(\\int \\cos x\\cdot \\mathrm{e}^{\\int \\tan x\\mathrm{d}x}\\mathrm{d}x + C\\right)\\cdot \\mathrm{e}^{-\\int \\tan x\\mathrm{d}x} = (x + C)\\cos x(C$ 为任意常数）.",
        "bbox": [
            204,
            510,
            811,
            536
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】1.",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            546,
            183,
            560
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】方法一 因为 $\\mathbf{A}$ 的任意两行都成比例，所以 $r(\\mathbf{A})\\leqslant 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            567,
            609,
            582
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "又因为 $\\mathbf{A} \\neq \\mathbf{0}$ , 所以 $r(\\mathbf{A}) \\geqslant 1$ , 故 $r(\\mathbf{A}) = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            589,
            458,
            603
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            611,
            150,
            623
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\mathbf {A} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{c} {a _ {1}} \\\\ {a _ {2}} \\\\ {\\vdots} \\\\ {a _ {n}} \\end{array} \\right] (b _ {1}, b _ {2}, \\dots , b _ {n}) = \\pmb {\\alpha} \\pmb {\\beta} ^ {\\mathrm {T}}, \\text {其 中} \\pmb {\\alpha} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{c} {a _ {1}} \\\\ {a _ {2}} \\\\ {\\vdots} \\\\ {a _ {n}} \\end{array} \\right], \\pmb {\\beta} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{c} {b _ {1}} \\\\ {b _ {2}} \\\\ {\\vdots} \\\\ {b _ {n}} \\end{array} \\right],\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            632,
            601,
            713
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nr (\\mathbf {A}) = r (\\boldsymbol {\\alpha} \\boldsymbol {\\beta} ^ {\\mathrm {T}}) \\leqslant r (\\boldsymbol {\\alpha}) = 1,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            721,
            338,
            735
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "再由 $a_{i}\\neq 0,b_{i}\\neq 0,i = 1,2,\\dots ,n$ 得 $\\mathbf{A}\\neq \\mathbf{O}$ ，于是 $r(A)\\geqslant 1$ ，故 $r(A) = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            744,
            706,
            757
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二、选择题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            57,
            764,
            146,
            780
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            786,
            204,
            800
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $\\lim_{x\\to 1^{-}}\\frac{x^2 - 1}{x - 1}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}} = 2\\lim_{x\\to 1^{-}}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}} = 0,$ $\\lim_{x\\to 1^{+}}\\frac{x^2 - 1}{x - 1}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}} = 2\\lim_{x\\to 1^{+}}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}} = +\\infty ,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            807,
            776,
            840
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "得 $\\lim_{x\\to 1}\\frac{x^2 - 1}{x - 1}\\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{1}{x - 1}}$ 不存在但不是 $\\infty$ ，应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            846,
            454,
            874
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（2）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            57,
            883,
            204,
            897
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\left|(-1)^n\\left(1 - \\cos \\frac{\\alpha}{n}\\right)\\right| = 2\\sin^2\\frac{\\alpha}{2n} \\sim \\frac{\\alpha^2}{2} \\cdot \\frac{1}{n^2},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            904,
            530,
            934
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\frac{\\alpha^2}{2} \\cdot \\frac{1}{n^2}$ 收敛，所以 $\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} \\left| (-1)^n \\left(1 - \\cos \\frac{\\alpha}{n}\\right) \\right|$ 收敛，即 $\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty} (-1)^n \\left(1 - \\cos \\frac{\\alpha}{n}\\right)$ 绝对收敛，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            69,
            873,
            124
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【答案】 （B）.",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            131,
            200,
            146
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 曲线的切线向量为 $\\pmb{T} = \\{1, -2t, 3t^2\\}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            82,
            152,
            466,
            167
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\{1, -2t, 3t^2\\} \\cdot \\{1, 2, 1\\} = 0$ 得 $t_1 = \\frac{1}{3}, t_2 = 1$ ，故与平面 $x + 2y + z = 4$ 平行的切线有2条，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            177,
            925,
            203
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            211,
            200,
            226
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $f(x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}2x^{3}, & x < 0,\\\\ 4x^{3}, & x\\geqslant 0, \\end{array} \\right.$ $f^{\\prime}(x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}6x^{2}. & x < 0,\\\\ 12x^{2}, & x > 0, \\end{array} \\right.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            233,
            584,
            271
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显然 $f^{\\prime}(0) = f^{\\prime \\prime}(0) = 0$ ， $f''(x) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}12x, & x <   0,\\\\ 24x, & x\\geqslant 0, \\end{array} \\right.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            280,
            528,
            313
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nf _ {-} ^ {\\prime \\prime} (0) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {-}} \\frac {f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x)}{x} = 1 2, \\quad f _ {+} ^ {\\prime \\prime} (0) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \\frac {f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x)}{x} = 2 4,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            320,
            549,
            354
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $f_{-}^{\\prime \\prime}(0)\\neq f_{+}^{\\prime \\prime}(0)$ ，所以 $f^{(n)}(0)$ 存在的最高阶数 $n = 2$ ，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            360,
            644,
            374
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】 （A).",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            383,
            202,
            396
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $\\xi_{1}$ 与 $\\xi_{2}$ 线性无关，所以三元齐次线性方程组 $AX = 0$ 的基础解系中至少含2个解向量，即 $3 - r(A)\\geqslant 2$ ，得 $r(\\mathbf{A})\\leqslant 1$ ，而选项(B)(C)(D)中矩阵的秩都大于1，所以均不对，只有选项（A）正确.三、",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            403,
            925,
            460
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【解】由 $1 - \\sqrt{1 - x^2} = -[(1 - x^2)^{\\frac{1}{2}} - 1] \\sim \\frac{1}{2} x^2 (x \\to 0)$ ，得",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            468,
            638,
            496
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - \\sin x - 1}{1 - \\sqrt {1 - x ^ {2}}} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - \\sin x - 1}{\\frac {1}{2} x ^ {2}} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} - \\cos x}{x} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} (\\mathrm {e} ^ {x} + \\sin x) = 1.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            506,
            743,
            550
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【解】 $\\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial x} = f_1' \\cdot \\mathrm{e}^x \\sin y + 2xf_2'$ ,",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            560,
            376,
            587
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\frac {\\partial^ {2} z}{\\partial x \\partial y} = e ^ {x} \\sin y \\cdot \\left(f _ {1 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\cdot e ^ {x} \\cos y + 2 y f _ {1 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}\\right) + f _ {1} ^ {\\prime} \\cdot e ^ {x} \\cos y + 2 x \\left(f _ {2 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} \\cdot e ^ {x} \\cos y + 2 y f _ {2 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}\\right) \\\\ = \\frac {1}{2} e ^ {2 x} \\sin 2 y \\cdot f _ {1 1} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + 2 e ^ {x} (y \\sin y + x \\cos y) f _ {1 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime} + f _ {1} ^ {\\prime} \\cdot e ^ {x} \\cos y + 4 x y f _ {2 2} ^ {\\prime \\prime}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            597,
            791,
            663
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【解】 $\\int_{1}^{3} f(x - 2) \\, \\mathrm{d}x = \\int_{1}^{3} f(x - 2) \\, \\mathrm{d}(x - 2) = \\int_{-1}^{1} f(x) \\, \\mathrm{d}x$ ",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            672,
            570,
            698
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= \\int_ {- 1} ^ {0} (1 + x ^ {2}) \\mathrm {d} x + \\int_ {0} ^ {1} \\mathrm {e} ^ {- x} \\mathrm {d} x = \\frac {7}{3} - \\frac {1}{\\mathrm {e}}.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            266,
            708,
            592,
            735
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "四、【解】 特征方程为 $\\lambda^2 + 2\\lambda - 3 = 0$ ，特征根为 $\\lambda_1 = -3, \\lambda_2 = 1$ ",
        "bbox": [
            53,
            744,
            615,
            759
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$y^{\\prime \\prime} + 2y^{\\prime} - 3y = 0$ 的通解为 $y = C_1\\mathrm{e}^{-3x} + C_2\\mathrm{e}^x$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            766,
            485,
            781
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $y^{\\prime \\prime} + 2y^{\\prime} - 3y = \\mathrm{e}^{-3x}$ 的特解为 $y_0(x) = ax\\mathrm{e}^{-3x}$ ，代入得 $a = -\\frac{1}{4}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            789,
            657,
            816
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $y^{\\prime \\prime} + 2y^{\\prime} - 3y = \\mathrm{e}^{-3x}$ 的通解为",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            825,
            361,
            840
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$y = C_{1}\\mathrm{e}^{-3x} + C_{2}\\mathrm{e}^{x} - \\frac{1}{4} x\\mathrm{e}^{-3x}(C_{1},C_{2}$ 为任意常数）.",
        "bbox": [
            289,
            849,
            716,
            875
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "五、【解】补充 $\\Sigma_{1}:z = 0(x^{2} + y^{2}\\leqslant a^{2})$ ，取下侧，",
        "bbox": [
            51,
            883,
            471,
            899
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nI = \\iint_ {\\Sigma} (x ^ {3} + a z ^ {2}) d y d z + (y ^ {3} + a x ^ {2}) d z d x + (z ^ {3} + a y ^ {2}) d x d y\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            154,
            905,
            661,
            937
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= \\left(\\iint_ {\\Sigma + \\Sigma_ {1}} - \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {1}}\\right) (x ^ {3} + a z ^ {2}) d y d z + (y ^ {3} + a x ^ {2}) d z d x + (z ^ {3} + a y ^ {2}) d x d y,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            179,
            70,
            754,
            106
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "而 $\\iint_{\\Sigma + \\Sigma_1} (x^3 + az^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}y \\, \\mathrm{d}z + (y^3 + ax^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}z \\, \\mathrm{d}x + (z^3 + ay^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y$ ",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            110,
            588,
            146
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} = 3 \\iiint_ {\\Omega} \\left(x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} + z ^ {2}\\right) \\mathrm {d} v = 3 \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} \\mathrm {d} \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} \\mathrm {d} \\varphi \\int_ {0} ^ {a} r ^ {4} \\sin \\varphi \\mathrm {d} r = \\frac {6 \\pi}{5} a ^ {5}, \\\\ \\iint_ {x _ {1}} \\left(x ^ {3} + a z ^ {2}\\right) d y d z + \\left(y ^ {3} + a x ^ {2}\\right) d z d x + \\left(z ^ {3} + a y ^ {2}\\right) d x d y \\\\ = \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {1}} a y ^ {2} d x d y = - a \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant a ^ {2}} y ^ {2} d x d y = - \\frac {a}{2} \\iint_ {x ^ {2} + y ^ {2} \\leqslant a ^ {2}} (x ^ {2} + y ^ {2}) d x d y \\\\ = - \\frac {a}{2} \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} \\mathrm {d} \\theta \\int_ {0} ^ {a} r ^ {3} \\mathrm {d} r = - \\frac {\\pi}{4} a ^ {5}, \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            110,
            642,
            300
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $\\iint_{\\Sigma} (x^3 + az^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}y \\, \\mathrm{d}z + (y^3 + ax^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}z \\, \\mathrm{d}x + (z^3 + ay^2) \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y = \\frac{6\\pi}{5} a^5 + \\frac{\\pi}{4} a^5 = \\frac{29}{20}\\pi a^5.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            309,
            789,
            341
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "六、【解】 不妨设 $0 < x_{1} < x_{2}$ ，由拉格朗日中值定理得",
        "bbox": [
            55,
            345,
            520,
            360
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$f(x_{1}) = f(x_{1}) - f(0) = f^{\\prime}(\\xi_{1})x_{1}$ ，其中 $0 < \\xi_{1} < x_{1}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            272,
            367,
            745,
            384
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$f(x_{1} + x_{2}) - f(x_{2}) = f^{\\prime}(\\xi_{2})x_{1}$ ，其中 $x_{2} <   \\xi_{2} <   x_{1} + x_{2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            256,
            388,
            764,
            405
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $f''(x) < 0$ ，所以 $f'(x)$ 单调递减，又因为 $\\xi_1 < \\xi_2$ ，所以 $f'(\\xi_1) > f'(\\xi_2)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            410,
            737,
            426
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
